      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ViewPatientPanel()
      The ViewPatientPanel() is the constructor which inherits froma a JPanel.When called, it constructs a JPanel that includes a number of components such as textfields and buttons that allow the user to view and edit a new patient's information.
